# Ollama AI (local docker)

## Management

### Pull a model into a docker container

```bash
docker exec -it ai-container-name ollama pull ollama-model
```

### Remove a model

```bash
docker exec -it ai-container-name ollama rm ollama-model-name
```

### See available commands of AI container

```bash
docker exec -it ai-container-name ollama --help
```

## restart docker containers

```bash
sudo systemctl restart docker
```
